## Usage

```jsx
<CopyButton text="Hello, world!" />
<CopyButton text="npm install my-package" />
```

## Key Features

✅ **Clipboard API** – Uses modern `navigator.clipboard.writeText()`  
✅ **Visual Feedback** – Color change + checkmark icon for 1.5 seconds  
✅ **ARIA Live Region** – Screen readers announce "Text copied to clipboard"  
✅ **No External State** – Uses only `useState` and `useRef`  
✅ **Timeout Cleanup** – Properly clears timeouts to prevent memory leaks  
✅ **Tailwind Styling** – Responsive, accessible color contrasts  
✅ **Semantic HTML** – Proper ARIA labels and button semantics

## Accessibility Highlights

- `aria-live="polite"` announces the copy success to screen readers
- `aria-atomic="true"` ensures the full message is read
- `sr-only` hides the live region visually while keeping it for assistive tech
- `aria-label` provides context for icon-based button
- Full keyboard support (built-in to `<button>`)
